          "question": "How quickly should I deploy this crisis communication plan?",
          "answer": "Speed is paramount in crisis communication. You should aim to deploy initial holding statements and the direct communication (email, blog post, initial social media alerts) within hours of confirming a security incident. Delays can lead to speculation, misinformation, and erosion of trust."
