      "sampleOutput": "```\nDISCOUNT CODE STRATEGY PLAN - \"Mastering AI Prompts\" Online Course Launch\n\n**I. Executive Summary**\nThis strategy aims to maximize conversions for \"Mastering AI Prompts\" while preserving its premium value. It leverages tiered discounts: an attractive early-bird offer for immediate adopters, unique codes for affiliate partners to incentivize their promotion, and a carefully timed flash sale to create urgency. The goal is to generate initial buzz, expand reach through partners, and capitalize on impulse purchases, all without resorting to deep, frequent discounting.\n\n**II. Discount Code Strategies**\n\n**1. Early Bird Discount (Launch Week 1)**\n*   **Objective:** Reward early adopters, generate initial sales momentum, and collect testimonials.\n*   **Code:** `AIPROMPTMASTER20`\n*   **Discount:** 20% off the full course price ($199 -> $159.20)\n*   **Conditions:** Valid for the first 7 days post-launch. Clearly communicate the expiry date.\n*   **Messaging:** \"Be among the first to master AI prompting! Save 20% with our exclusive early bird offer.\"\n*   **Placement:** Prominently featured on landing page, launch emails, and social media.\n*   **Perceived Value Management:** Frame it as a special reward for your loyal audience, not a permanent price reduction.\n\n**2. Affiliate Partner Program (Ongoing Post-Early Bird)**\n*   **Objective:** Leverage trusted voices to expand reach and drive sales through commissions.\n*   **Code Structure:** Unique codes for each affiliate, e.g., `AIPROMPT[AFFILIATENAME]15` (e.g., `AIPROMPTJOHN15`).\n*   **Discount:** 15% off the full course price ($199 -> $169.15)\n*   **Conditions:** Codes are tied to specific affiliates for tracking. Commissions based on sales attributed to their unique code.\n*   **Messaging (for affiliates):** \"Offer your audience an exclusive 15% discount on 'Mastering AI Prompts' and earn a commission on every sale!\"\n*   **Placement:** Affiliates share their unique code with their audience.\n*   **Perceived Value Management:** Positions the course as valuable enough for partners to promote at a slightly reduced rate, indicating desirability.\n\n**3. Limited-Time Flash Sale (Post-Launch, Week 4-5)**\n*   **Objective:** Drive a surge in sales for those who missed early-bird or affiliate offers, create urgency.\n*   **Code:** `AIPROMPTFLASH25`\n*   **Discount:** 25% off the full course price ($199 -> $149.25)\n*   **Conditions:** Very short window (e.g., 48-72 hours only). Strict expiry.\n*   **Messaging:** \"Last chance to unlock your AI potential! Grab 'Mastering AI Prompts' for 25% off – ends in 48 hours!\"\n*   **Placement:** Email list, social media, pop-up on sales page.\n*   **Perceived Value Management:** The limited duration reinforces the idea that this is an exceptional, temporary offer, not the new normal price. Avoid frequent flash sales.\n\n**III. Overall Considerations**\n*   **Pricing Anchor:** Always display the full course price prominently to establish value before showing the discounted price.\n*   **Exclusivity:** Emphasize the \"exclusive\" nature of the discounts where applicable.\n*   **Tracking:** Ensure your e-commerce platform can track conversions by specific discount codes.\n*   **Sequencing:** Maintain a clear sequence for discount rollout to avoid devaluing early bird offers.\n*   **Avoid Over-Discounting:** Frequent or deep discounts can train customers to wait for sales, harming perceived value.\n```",
